text: Onepoto may refer to: * Onepoto, Hawke's Bay, a small settlement near Lake Waikaremoana * Onepoto, Wellington, a suburb of Porirua, New Zealand * Onepoto (volcanic crater), a feature near Northcote in Auckland, New Zealand * Onepoto Bridge, a bridge in Auckland, New Zealand * Te Onepoto / Taylors Mistake is a beach and bach community on Banks Peninsula, New Zealand
title: Onepoto
